title: Men in front of time board at Kooskia
description: A photograph of the work projects check-in board. This insured that all individuals out on a project were accounted for when not in camp, and could be used as a means of tracking who had not returned at days end. Photo taken from 12-3/4 x 15-1/4 Photograph album of the Kooskia Japanese Internment Camp.
